—ظWarchive/external_nushell_repo_backup/nushell.github.io/commands/docs/attr_deprecated.mdظ@066b87438dfd24da004c3ca069ba7d703d00bcc9bc81518c0b2cc8096708f6d3¶title: attr deprecated‘¨ExamplesعBAdd a deprecation warning to a custom command.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> @deprecated
    def outdated [] {}


```
Add a deprecation warning with a custom message.
